    "notes": "Game crashes immediately when starting a new game or loading saves with EXCEPTION_ACCESS_VIOLATION in d3d12core.dll at offset +36363D.\n\n**Root Cause:** Starfield requests D3D12 interface {0742a90b-c387-483f-b946-30a7e4e61458} (likely ID3D12Device10/Work Graphs) which VKD3D-Proton 3.0 doesn't implement. When VKD3D returns E_NOINTERFACE, the game crashes with a null pointer dereference instead of handling it gracefully.\n\n**Tested (All Failed):**\n- GE-Proton 10-27 + VKD3D_FEATURE_LEVEL=12_0\n- VKD3D_SHADER_MODEL=6_6 override\n- VKD3D_CONFIG=no_upload_hvv + disabled extensions\n- DRI_PRIME=1 for dGPU selection\n- Removed/overrode NVIDIA Streamline DLLs\n- Reset StarfieldPrefs.ini to safe defaults\n\n**Conclusion:** Game likely requires newer D3D12 Agility SDK features not yet supported in VKD3D-Proton. Unplayable until VKD3D adds missing interface support.",
